Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:04.38,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Two people's deductions and suspense\Nfill the gulf between love and hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:06.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today, it's Chinatown in Yokohama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:08.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The surprising people Ran got involved with!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:09.73,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.78,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who presented the "Opinion on Twelve Matters" to Emperor Daigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiyoyuki Miyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the term for a Pureland Buddhist painting that depicts the descent of Buddha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoju Raigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Can you knock it off?\NThat stuff gives me hives!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a big Japanese history test tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I've been too busy with karate to study for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you should've stayed home tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who won us that free meal at Chinatown Restaurant, may I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're telling me to stay home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay! Just shut the book until we get home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I won't have time to study tonight!\NThere's a ton of great stuff on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reading in the car is gonna make you carsick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I've got a tough semicircular canal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's starting to rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:51.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's raining pretty hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:56.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}For some reason, it brings back memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That man in the cap, standing in the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:08.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I can't remember {\i1}where{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:12.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A back street in an unfamiliar city...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:17.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why can't I remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:22.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Every time I try, I just see that image of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Standing in the rain, just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:33.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the look on Shin'ichi's face, kind but sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why are you drenched in rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:39.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tell me, Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your forehead went all wrinkly and your face got scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:56.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't remember the answer to this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the Cloistered Rule Period,\NKiyohira Fujiwara...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nuts. Guess I {\i1}have{\i0} gotten carsick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as we're about to start filming,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,our lead actress breaks a bone in a motorcycle accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should just stop trying to make this movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:40.34,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kaizo Isogami (52)\NMovie Director
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to be cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, we can't pass up an opportunity like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the sequel to a blockbuster, and it's already attracting buzz!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:56.94,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Motohiro Ito (38)\NAssistant Director
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With our actress injured, we're stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the only girl we've found who can play this role!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:04.95,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Keigo Kitaura (29)\NOriginal Author
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we keep trying to film this picture, the body count...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,will only go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm glad that actress pulled out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She never fit my image of the heroine of my novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kitaura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn... Why can't we find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:25.97,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shiro Kawabata (46)\NProducer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cute young girl, who can handle action scenes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, we can't use this gift certificate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the restaurant's name is written right on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:40.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's us... We issued the coupon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why can't we use it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I demand an explanation and a clear one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kiddo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's your sister's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of joint is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you pick your customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No! Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You snobs think you can mess with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take this outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't try to strong-arm us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not going anywhere until we get an explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your sister's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-The certificate says clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's not valid on Sundays or holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's right! It's here in the small print!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no... I sincerely apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. We're happy that you understand the provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, why didn't you check in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say what? You're the one who rushed out first, saying that early bird catches the worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, young lady, that was a good kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about you and me going to see a Bruce Lee movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:28.18,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mike Hama\NPrivate Eye
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Mike Hama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not kidding, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mike Hama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard that name before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This guy is Mike Hama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got an office on the second floor of Yokohama Nichigeki in Kogane-cho...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That second-rate private eye who has an office on the second floor of a movie theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... that's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, lady, call me when you feel like going out with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you later, kiddo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your dinner, sir... What would you like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you join us for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll pick up the check!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A heroine in a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're perfect for the role!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're interested in the part...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll just forget your lines and make a laughingstock of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not everyone is blessed with my oratory skills, my power to entrance a crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:56.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Your power to {\i1}sleep{\i0}, while I put on a show for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if the movie's a hit, you'll be a star! You'll be in showbiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll hobnob with movie stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention baseball players, soccer stars, Formula 1 drivers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll travel the world for the film. America, England, France...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Go for it, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go for it! Take on challenges!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you're going to do it,\Nyou'd better be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. Some filmmakers will completely ignore the original story
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to add a racy love scene or similar junk...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-Love scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kitaura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}! You're not talking about {\i1}me{\i0}, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On second thought, say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's all wrong for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if doing one little love scene scares you, don't sign on for this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show business can be the death of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop scaring her! This girl here is our golden goose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way... I'm nothing special...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I'll just wipe it up with my hot towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Can I get a new pair of chopsticks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:27.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got a fever. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine! It's just a little head cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what if you collapse like last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't listen to your hard-headed dad! Talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you want and I'll bring it to you on a platter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! I thought I said not to order the century eggs or the crab omelette!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm allergic to eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't even stand to {\i1}look{\i0} at egg dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, young lady, eat all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want curry with rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid, this is a Chinese restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't have curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I want curry! Curry, curry, curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they don't have curry, I don't wanna eat here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think we should go home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here! Have some Chinese dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really liked these the last time we had them, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:01.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez. Doesn't she care about my feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:04.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh well. Where's the soy sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah, in front of the old guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:11.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:15.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn. It's in front of the old guy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:17.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? Do you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, the soy sauce...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:32.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Okay, the chili oil is in front of that fox-faced guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here! You want the chili oil, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She has to do everything for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Peking duck here is superb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you have any favorite actresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One is Yukiko Fujimine{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the mother of one of my best friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I've looked up to her since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the other?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other is an American actress...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sharon Vineyard{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she passed away a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! A great actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! I met her once and she was really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey where'd you meet a star like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nowhere you'd know, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukiko Fujimine and Sharon Vineyard? You've got taste, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're both legendary performers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she hadn't died, she might've become a legend like those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is Shiro Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age 46, a movie producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death seems to be asphyxiation caused by potassium cyanide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly. Potassium cyanide, arsenic, caustic soda...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do criminals keep getting their hands on this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:33.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did this guy put anything into his mouth before he dropped dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Peking duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The waiter wrapped the duck in crêpes and placed them on the plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim went into convulsions the moment he bit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So his last supper was Peking duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least he went out on a high note.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no poison was found in the Peking duck,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the waiter didn't have any cyanide on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:15:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so the victim must've had the poison on his hands before he picked up the duck crêpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the person who poisoned this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is one of you guys who were eating with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you guys know the stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're in the movie biz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The star of our latest project got in an accident before we started shooting,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and we were discussing what to do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we find a replacement, or ditch the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this girl and her family walked in, and Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} saw something in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He invited them to come have dinner with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! You with the mustache! I've seen you before...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:48.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course you have! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're an ex-con, right?\NOr a wanted man on the run?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not! I'm Kogoro Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:16:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mouri? You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As in the famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's me, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that cheap con man called "Smoking Kogoro", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}Sleeping{\i0} Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! We've got a cyanide reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't find any traces of poison in the other dishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we've found evidence of potassium cyanide
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,on the chopsticks, plate and hot towel the victim was using.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially the towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was sitting next to the victim when he collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sitting on his right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And on his left?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sitting to his left, eating dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this case is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer poisoned his own towel and switched it with the victim's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you, Mr. Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't suspect a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you were on his right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the victim was right-handed, he would've placed his towel right next to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew he'd wipe his hands on the towel before picking up the duck crêpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fess up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't I seen {\i1}you{\i0} somewhere too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't try to change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he looks familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've never met! I just know your face from TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yokomizo! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yokomizo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Inspector Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were forced to shave your head because you screwed up a case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need to be embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I like the new look better than that doofy old perm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:18:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're talking about my twin brother Sango! He works for the Shizuoka Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:04.11,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Jugo Yokomizo\NKanazawa Prefectural Police\NInspector
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Jugo Yokomizo, an inspector for the Kanagawa Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're brothers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother is easy-going and seems to respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't trust private eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you make of this mark on the victim's jeans?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like some kind of stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I spilled it on him when I was sitting next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You were next to the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you and the kid were sitting next to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} switched seats. He forced himself between me and Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, Conan sat next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So before he moved, he was sitting between the girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:19:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I ended up next to him after Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} invited the detective to the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the detective and his family joined us, Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was sitting between him and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but our chairs were pretty far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I was on the other side of the table the whole time. I'm innocent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll know {\i1}after{\i0} the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you check his trousers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawabata{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} changed seats after the soup was spilled,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he used his towel to wipe it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you check the stain, you can see whether the towel was poisoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Uncle Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? There's no trace of poison on his trousers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you checked?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, the waiter told us he gave the victim a fresh pair of chopsticks
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after his first ones fell on the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we didn't find any cyanide on the chopsticks either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:20:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the towel was poisoned {\i1}after{\i0} the soup was spilled,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the waiter brought the new chopsticks and the victim switched seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you're still the chief suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I poison a guy I'd just met at a restaurant I'd never been to before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But your story sounds too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The minute you show up at this place, your daughter gets scouted for a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a total coincidence that we came here the same time as...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:57.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:21:02.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After all, I met that man on a rainy night...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:03.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:08.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe he just looks like somebody I know, like that inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:11.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why can't I remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:15.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All I can dredge up are three faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A smiling mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:22.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Angry eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:27.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:30.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:36.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't hear you, Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm okay! Just felt a little dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a seat! I'm sure Uncle will crack the case soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.42,0:21:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And don't get in the way, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:06.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:10.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran's acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:14.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We have to get her to a hospital soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.50,0:23:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You took the towel into the restroom and poisoned it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.57,0:23:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:58.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can't even stand to look at them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there anything else on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm, I see... Nothing else on it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:16.85,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hot towel
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.87,0:24:24.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Mike Hama, Private Eye", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.65,0:24:26.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The old guy's got the same nonchalance, at least.
